folder: Sand Lane & Cedar Avenue, Staten Island, NY
text:
Sand Lane, east side, between Cedar Avenue and Robin Road, showing rooming houses in Arrochar
Village. The view is south.
1923
P. L. Sperr

text:

(2)
The rectory, at number 203 Sand Lane, and the
church, looking down the east side of the Lane.
